ncmeta
  • Reference

File info

Get information about a NetCDF data source, may be a file path, or a RNetCDF file handle, or an Thredds server address.

nc_inq(x, ...)

# S3 method for NetCDF
nc_inq(x, ...)

# S3 method for character
nc_inq(x, ...)

Arguments

x

filename or handle
...

ignored

Examples

#f <- raadfiles:::cmip5_files()$fullname[1]
#nc_inq(f)
#nc_var(f, 0)
#nc_dim(f, 0)
f <- system.file("extdata", "S2008001.L3m_DAY_CHL_chlor_a_9km.nc", package = "ncmeta")
nc_inq(f)
#> # A tibble: 1 x 5
#>   ndims nvars ngatts unlimdimid
#>   <dbl> <dbl>  <dbl>      <lgl>
#> 1     4     4     65         NA
#> # ... with 1 more variables: filename <chr>
nc_var(f, 0)
#> # A tibble: 2 x 6
#>      id    name     type ndims dimids natts
#>   <dbl>   <chr>    <chr> <dbl>  <dbl> <dbl>
#> 1     0 chlor_a NC_FLOAT     2      1    12
#> 2     0 chlor_a NC_FLOAT     2      0    12
nc_dim(f, 0)
#> # A tibble: 1 x 4
#>      id  name length unlim
#> * <dbl> <chr>  <dbl> <lgl>
#> 1     0   lat   2160 FALSE

nc_vars(f)
#> # A tibble: 6 x 6
#>      id    name     type ndims dimids natts
#>   <dbl>   <chr>    <chr> <dbl>  <dbl> <dbl>
#> 1     0 chlor_a NC_FLOAT     2      1    12
#> 2     0 chlor_a NC_FLOAT     2      0    12
#> 3     1     lat NC_FLOAT     1      0     5
#> 4     2     lon NC_FLOAT     1      1     5
#> 5     3 palette  UNKNOWN     2      3     0
#> 6     3 palette  UNKNOWN     2      2     0
nc_dims(f)
#> # A tibble: 4 x 4
#>      id          name length unlim
#>   <dbl>         <chr>  <dbl> <lgl>
#> 1     0           lat   2160 FALSE
#> 2     1           lon   4320 FALSE
#> 3     2           rgb      3 FALSE
#> 4     3 eightbitcolor    256 FALSE
